man_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://huiji-thumb.huijistatic.com/warcraft/uploads/thumb/0/05/Raneman_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg/270px-Raneman_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"https://huiji-thumb.huijistatic.com/warcraft/uploads/thumb/0/05/Raneman_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg/405px-Raneman_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg 1.5x, https://huiji-thumb.huijistatic.com/warcraft/uploads/thumb/0/05/Raneman_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg/540px-Raneman_Anniversary_Artwork.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1200\" data-file-height=\"801\"></a></div></div>\n			<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>玛维与《<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%BA%89%E9%9C%B8III\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"魔兽争霸III\">魔兽争霸III</a>》的其他英雄。\n</p>\n			</div>\n		</div></li>\n		<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 222.66666666667px\"><div style=\"width: 222.66666666667px\">\n			<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 220.66666666667px;\"><div style=\"margin:0px auto;\"><a href=\"/wiki/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6:The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://huiji-thumb.huijistatic.com/warcraft/uploads/thumb/8/8c/The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg/331px-The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg\" width=\"221\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"https://huiji-thumb.huijistatic.com/warcraft/uploads/thumb/8/8c/The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg/497px-The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg 1.5x, https://huiji-thumb.huijistatic.com/warcraft/uploads/thumb/8/8c/The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg/662px-The_Return_by_KoniArt.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"800\" data-file-height=\"435\"></a></div></div>\n			<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>KoniArt的“归来”，其中的守望者可能就是玛维。\n</p>\n			</div>\n		</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8F.82.E8.80.83.E4.B8.8E.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">参考与注释</span></h2>\n<div style=\"font-size:14px;\">\n<div class=\"reflist columns references-column-count references-column-count-2\" style=\"-moz-column-count: 2; -webkit-column-count: 2; column-count: 2; list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-referen